title: News, TNF preview & Warner on Geno
itunes:title: News, TNF preview & Warner on Geno
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest NFL news including Ryan Tannehill's situation in Miami and the Le'Veon Bell hype train. The guys also preview the Giants vs. Redskins TNF matchup and discuss Geno Smith with former Super Bowl MVP, Kurt Warner.
